{"name":"Maximize Magic","type":"advance","img":"icons/magic/perception/hand-eye-pink.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.kdvcKgW7rNJwM4Vd"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-b5086c91-7fff-77bf-1dcf-9e8bb1f51ea1\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">0 HP, 3 F</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Active, Psionic, Rank 1</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">When you cast a psionic spell, you can expend one additional increment of focus to use the maximum value for each die roll to determine the effects or duration of the spell instead of rolling it.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","xpCost":300,"hpBonus":0,"fpBonus":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774472156149,"modifiedTime":1774472156149,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"eMRwWqnKnFuDg687"}
{"name":"Quicken Magic","type":"advance","img":"icons/magic/sonic/projectile-sound-rings-wave.webp","effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.VxGFDqBC5dca4Opv"}},"system":{"tier":1,"name":"","description":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Active, Psionic, Rank 1</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-4fa3ea75-7fff-e677-0c0e-8bdcda20d81d\"></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Merriweather,serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">When you cast a psionic spell that costs 2 or more AP, you can expend one additional increment of focus to reduce the AP cost of that spell by 1.</span></p>","xpCost":300,"hpBonus":0,"fpBonus":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"ashen","systemVersion":"0.3.2","coreVersion":"10.312","createdTime":1774472157644,"modifiedTime":1774472157644,"lastModifiedBy":"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"3coP1hWuS5N2Xu17":3},"_id":"w22uBsKye87rIDHi"}
